ike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:06:41.000Z","msg":"最撚討厭既係<br />\n呢度d人為屌而屌<br />\n咩全部女人都係雞，少少嘢就比人擺上黎公審<br />\n之前我都好憎KOL，但依家覺得人地貪心又好，點都好，關我咩事呢，唔睇咪算囉。<br />\n依家又出賣女友又借人黎公審咁，真係好悶。"},{"pid":"9804a74589c90bc43dea66eee47d7b0ece82f33b","tid":426071,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:08:20.000Z","msg":"咁似之前某xx郎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213f1a986fdf43ab5e4bcac8fb0b23b1e8fefc39","tid":426071,"uid":79932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"快心 我會追晒你之前啲故"},{"pid":"3e72a4f18d56f1a0ffe7baaa1e8f7c11db6dce04","tid":426071,"uid":79932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快心 我會追晒你之前啲故</blockquote><br />\n放心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3afac11a5ec31c38d92229748abe62e8455083","tid":426071,"uid":1412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:12:34.000Z","msg":"下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5222099dfe73b972a26a28ae6d8e571999815d2f","tid":426071,"uid":45173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快心 我會追晒你之前啲故</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打"},{"pid":"cdab510794515226d000143f1a5f18ce3f99137a","tid":426071,"uid":47268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:39:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>回家吧啦</blockquote><br />\n回家係高質d但又要比joe joe撚</blockquote><br />\n啊joe可能會改"},{"pid":"324e4d861e1792f8415937e1c39cbaef209b9d65","tid":426071,"uid":53886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:45:54.000Z","msg":"唔好走啦 我留言啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor